                  <foliation type="ancient"/>
                  <collation>
                    <p>The quires seem to have been signed with both letters and arithmetical figures (see <locus from="204">fol. 204</locus>)</p>
                  </collation>
                  <condition>
                    <p>Several quires are either wanting or defective</p>
                    <p>This manuscript is very imperfect, the following portions of the text being now missing: ch. 3:6—15, 4:6—10:25, 10:33—42, 13:12—23, 13:32—14:8, 15:19—16:3, 21:44—22:16, and 24:9 to the end.</p>
                  </condition>
